
= a card deck to set up and manage projects ?

=Description=

Ola Möller:

"MethodKit is a tool that gives space for interpretation. There is no right or wrong way to use them. The cards are basically icons and headlines with important aspects you need to think about when you do a project or when you think about yourself and where you are going. The hundreds of interviews I did really helped in getting an understanding for how people think. This is not based on academia and theories. This is based on the intuitive. The synthesis of something I brought from my own and other people’s experiences. I always liked being philosophic. I do the thinking for my own pleasure. MethodKit is my own need for making an output from that fluff. An output that is extremely tangible and usable from that very philosophic process."

